// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1084 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: a49aebc8-af46-56f5-8b89-3ec021e58e01

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
